# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Inyuku Digital — environment variable template.
# Copy to .env.local and fill with real values. NEVER commit .env.local.
# Vite reads VITE_-prefixed vars today; the Next.js migration (M0-B) will
# rename client vars to NEXT_PUBLIC_ and move server vars server-side.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# App
VITE_APP_ENV=development            # development | staging | production
VITE_APP_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Auth vendor — PENDING EA-ADR-014 (Clerk carve-out vs in-house JWT). Do not pre-commit.
# Database / Storage vendor — PENDING EA-ADR-014 (Supabase-as-Postgres, EU-pinned, Prisma SoT).
# AI — routes via the portfolio lib/ai.js gateway (EA-ADR-009/011/012), not a direct vendor key here.

# Observability — added during M1
# SENTRY_DSN=
